{"name": "django-objectid", "metadata": {"name": "django-objectid", "version": "1.0.9", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/tangdyy/django-objectid", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["django"], "summary": "django objectid", "upload_time": 1735438339}, "documentation": ["# Django-objectid\r\n\r\nDjango-objectid\u7528\u4e8eDjango\u6846\u67b6\u5728\u5206\u5e03\u5f0f\u73af\u5883\u4e2d\u9ad8\u6548\u751f\u6210\u4e0d\u91cd\u590dID\u503c\u3002\r\n\r\n### \u4f9d\u8d56\r\n+ django >= 2.2.0\r\n\r\n### \u5b89\u88c5\r\n+ pip\u5b89\u88c5\r\n```shell\r\npip install django-objectid\r\n```\r\n+ \u6e90\u7801\u5b89\u88c5\r\n```shell\r\npython setup.py install\r\n```\r\n### \u53d1\u5e03\u5305\r\n```shell\r\n# \u6253\u5305\r\npython setup.py bdist_wheel\r\n# \u4e0a\u4f20\r\ntwine upload -u xxx -p ***  ./dist/*\r\n```\r\n\r\n### \u4f7f\u7528\r\nDjango-objectid\u5305\u62ec\u4e24\u4e2a\u7c7b\uff0c`ObjectID`\uff0c`ObjectidModel`\u3002\r\n##### class objectid.ObjectID(id=None)\r\n\u751f\u6210\u3001\u89e3\u6790objectid\u3002\r\n\u53c2\u6570id\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u957f\u5ea6\u4e3a24\u7684\u5b57\u7b26\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u662f`None`\u5219\u751f\u6210\u65b0\u7684ObjectID\u5b9e\u4f8b\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e00\u4e2a\u6709\u6548ID\u5219\u89e3\u6790\u8fd9\u4e2aID\u4e3aObjectID\u5b9e\u4f8b\u3002ObjectID\u5b9e\u4f8b\u6709\u5982\u4e0b\u5c5e\u6027\uff1a\r\n+ `timestamp`\uff0cID\u4e2d\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u6233\uff0c\u4e5f\u5c31\u662fID\u521b\u5efa\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u3002 \r\n+ `host`\uff0cID\u4e2d\u7684\u4e3b\u673a\u540d\uff0c\u662f\u5b9e\u9645\u4e3b\u673a\u540d\u7ecf\u8fc7\u54c8\u5e0c\u5904\u7406\u540e\u7684\u503c\u3002\r\n+ `pid`\uff0c\u8fdb\u7a0bID\uff0c\u53ef\u80fd\u4e0e\u5b9e\u9645\u503c\u4e0d\u4e00\u81f4\u3002\r\n+ `count`\uff0c\u540c\u4e00\u8fdb\u7a0b\u4e00\u79d2\u5185\u751f\u6210\u7684ID\u5e8f\u53f7\u3002\r\n\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom objectid import ObjectID, create_objectid\r\n# \u521b\u5efaID\u5bf9\u8c61\r\nid = ObjectID()\r\n# \u83b7\u5f97id\u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\r\nidstr = str(id)\r\n# \u76f4\u63a5\u521b\u5efaid\u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\r\nidstr = create_objectid()\r\n# \u89e3\u6790id\u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\r\nid = ObjectID('5fb1ee9af1d79721f0000015')\r\n```\r\n#### class objectid.ObjectidModel()\r\n`ObjectidModel`\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u62bd\u8c61\u7c7b\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u5355\u72ec\u4f7f\u7528\uff0c\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5b9a\u4e49django\u6a21\u578b\u7c7b\u7684\u57fa\u7c7b\u3002\u5b9e\u4f8b\u5bf9\u8c61\u6709\u5982\u4e0b\u5c5e\u6027\u548c\u65b9\u6cd5\uff1a\r\n+ get_id_datetime()\uff0c\u8fd4\u56deid\u4e2d\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u6233\u3002\r\n+ \u591a\u6570\u636e\u4e2d\u5fc3\u5e03\u7f72\u65f6\uff0csettings\u4e2d\u589e\u52a0\u914d\u7f6e `DCID`\uff0c\u6570\u636e\u4e2d\u5fc3ID\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u4e3a0\u3002\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "objectid.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "objectid.utils.lock_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fo", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "flags", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.unlock_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fo", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.lock_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fo", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "flags", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.unlock_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fo", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "objectid.utils.LOCK_EX", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.LOCK_SH", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.LOCK_NB", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "objectid.utils.__overlapped", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "ex